### 7. Create Flashcard
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flashcards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic_id": 1,
  "front_text": "1/2 + 1/4 ?",
  "back_text": "3/4"
}

### 8. Create Quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quizzes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic_id": 1,
  "question_text": "Simplify 1/2 + 1/4",
